# DevOps CI/CD Pipeline Assignment

## Project Overview

This project demonstrates a complete DevOps CI/CD pipeline implementation using:

* Git & GitHub
* Jenkins
* Docker
* DockerHub
* AWS EC2
* Kubernetes
* Prometheus
* Grafana

The pipeline automatically:

1. Pulls source code from GitHub
2. Builds Docker image
3. Runs basic tests
4. Pushes Docker image to DockerHub
5. Deploys containerized application to AWS EC2
6. Monitors application using Prometheus and Grafana

---

# CI/CD Architecture

```text
Developer Push Code
        ↓
GitHub Repository
        ↓
GitHub Webhook Trigger
        ↓
Jenkins Pipeline
        ↓
Checkout Source Code
        ↓
Build Docker Image
        ↓
Run Tests
        ↓
Push Docker Image to DockerHub
        ↓
Deploy Container to AWS EC2
        ↓
Monitor using Prometheus & Grafana
```

