# Step 17: Configure GitHub Webhook

Configured GitHub webhook to automatically trigger Jenkins pipeline when code is pushed.

Webhook URL:

```text
http://EC2_PUBLIC_IP:8080/github-webhook/
```

Webhook Event:

```text
Just the push event
```

